{"tid":312394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遼寧號水線下甩漆生銹 黃東：保養實在有啲那個！","createTime":"2017-07-07T11:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T19:18:20.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4b6b89492a1f8397b495a1d8bca4cb7d83bfd4","tid":312394,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:50:46.000Z","msg":"中國第一艘航空母艦遼寧號今日訪港，可是不少細節卻反映解放軍仍未能做好細節。澳門國際軍事學會會長黃東表示，觀看航母進入香港時的照片，發現艦身水線下面紅色的防銹漆部份出現甩漆、生銹，相當明顯。黃東認為這樣的細節顯示這艘航母的保養「實在有啲那個」。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱：「你睇佢有幾打得，就係睇佢呢啲細節！細節決定成敗！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499408475_358e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499408475_358e.jpg&h=b3cf5486&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"254f0abd3511367d42c82b9f1a9f2092099512ca","tid":312394,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16a4bc272e1965351494ac165805f86f559d5c88","tid":312394,"uid":105062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"84eb416144aece658cdc6e7e226addf0048e9daf","tid":312394,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"突登的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一航母維修保養至少半年<br />\n<br />\n家下大陸極缺艦載機員<br />\n<br />\n半年已經可以訓練不少飛機起降/機員<br />\n<br />\n所以是時間問題<br />\n<br />\n其實大陸月月都有軍艦下水<br />\n<br />\n錢大撚把"},{"pid":"6e1bca7c62ca87a016b4c5d242b5cc7f27609cd7","tid":312394,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"這是中國人航母特色 你懂個屁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae00e25032ab1589673b33d23ce5cb241778d6f","tid":312394,"uid":122718,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"756f360d7aa14f7c928135b2269db5906ad0e60a","tid":312394,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有支激光槍可以清銹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尋晚東張西望講嗰支淘寶貨呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bb1cadc1f9dd07f6a55dae11bf144d90239d62","tid":312394,"uid":4493,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國第一艘航空母艦遼寧號今日訪港，可是不少細節卻反映解放軍仍未能做好細節。澳門國際軍事學會會長黃東表示，觀看航母進入香港時的照片，發現艦身水線下面紅色的防銹漆部份出現甩漆、生銹，相當明顯。黃東認為這樣的細節顯示這艘航母的保養「實在有啲那個」。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱：「你睇佢有幾打得，就係睇佢呢啲細節！細節決定成敗！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499408475_358e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499408475_358e.jpg&h=b3cf5486&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個〈黃東〉真係〈含得能橡皮糖〉！<br />\n睇過佢唔少評論大陸，每次都係為反，而反，<br />\n清除嗰啲〈鏽色〉要大修入〈塢〉才做到！<br />\n唔係派啲船員放〈繩梯〉可做到，軍事專家？<br />\n〈磚家〉就真，唔識？上網查囉，咪亂發.噏風，<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">有圖有真相....去相..........</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/201208_51fa4f4d5c36e54c460ba8d3d88f7665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F201208_51fa4f4d5c36e54c460ba8d3d88f7665.jpg&h=c4107741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人哋個里數係你幾百倍<br />\n服役時間係你十幾倍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">生銹都係冇你咁勁<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知醜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"63ff47aebb48176435cd703d77f11be8d88b4f1f","tid":312394,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2113d1ff7eed62935c5c4033f19ce875f34f4545","tid":312394,"uid":122718,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae4b59893ba4024baedb2c341dec996e5464d2b0","tid":312394,"uid":10890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"所有話一定會生鏽嗰啲<br />\n留意返隻船已經大執過先落水<br />\n到底係落水前就生鏽甩油<br />\n定係行咗一段咁短時間就生鏽甩油呢？<br />\n是但一樣都可以貽笑大方"},{"pid":"28546ce58dc8540393f1f3c6c8641f8de0b2bb79","tid":312394,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:06:38.000Z","msg":"洩露國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fb3ec6d677c80dcdee2a01627613477e0f4f4f","tid":312394,"uid":122718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:08:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5079618db5c95879dcb464afa88dfdb316458c25","tid":312394,"uid":122718,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"213db0fe3f983db73e46bd9d9f849c50fa32d42b","tid":312394,"uid":122718,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e40279980a7ddb39f84f7419d777098919d0fb5f","tid":312394,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所有話一定會生鏽嗰啲<br />\n留意返隻船已經大執過先落水<br />\n到底係落水前就生鏽甩油<br />\n定係行咗一段咁短時間就生鏽甩油呢？<br />\n是但一樣都可以貽笑大方</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/210808_51fa4f4d5c36e54c460ba8d3d88f7665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eser