quote>水線上生鏽同水線下生鏽邊個攞命啲都分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大大張圖自己又唔擘大對屎眼睇<br />\n人地係上面有鏽水流落嚟下面<br />\n支那就直接喺水線打落生鏽<br />\n五毛繼續兜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五毛係咁上下，陣間沉撚左都有得兜，返屋企拎支五星旗抹返D精啦"},{"pid":"e1998024bfd10e4a1a9e2d9f3c6ed365fadc562c","tid":312394,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"一入到黎已經見到兩個show blocked user<br />\n就知道呢個post 唔駛睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf5cba875b35aec9922a46c4f3c09b34e61ec82","tid":312394,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"Impressed current cathodic protection system (ICCP)<br />\n<br />\n但燒重油就算鳩數吧啦....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地核動力先玩得起ICCP"},{"pid":"fdeeaa0ff688c2a91ebf53357bf78b93f203b68d","tid":312394,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"兩條友打晒飛機<br />\n<br />\n係咪中銀返工"},{"pid":"9b8d6b6b17a5dfa256766336691d2f395f52683d","tid":312394,"uid":122718,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba983c56845464ae4245342b4888a17ffca7dc0e","tid":312394,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"又係大字有色五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ed49e2f0f6b803f754bc99157de5ff140461c2","tid":312394,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"北洋水師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd9076d137d1406014353f083ad02f020c0ea6b","tid":312394,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揾嚟搞 返夜工 辛唔辛苦? <br />\n<br />\n做五毛 真係唔容易, E家仲要識MARK圖</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">嘈乜柒姐屌你老母死五毛，兩隻艦連埋艦隊打過囉</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829f331cd495f823e4a0426446f1f230e3405878","tid":312394,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <blockquote><blockquote>水線上生鏽同水線下生鏽邊個攞命啲都分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大大張圖自己又唔擘大對屎眼睇<br />\n人地係上面有鏽水流落嚟下面<br />\n支那就直接喺水線打落生鏽<br />\n五毛繼續兜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">haha你真係要..擘大對屎眼慢慢睇，<br />\n兩張相有何不同，船身都會生鏽？<br />\n水線打下無生鏽？識唔識放大相呀，</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/212652_51fa4f4d5c36e54c460ba8d3d88f7665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F212652_51fa4f4d5c36e54c460ba8d3d88f7665.jpg&h=b0aaec9c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">船嘅〈水線〉長期浸在海水中唔會〈生鏽〉？<br />\n船身有幾何有海水浸到？竟會〈生鏽〉？<br />\n你自己擘大啲個屎眼睇清楚，再唔係早啲瞓喇！</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n都係美帝既錯。<br />\n美帝航母唔應該出洋。D海水拍到上甲板。都係美帝維護唔好。俾D海水打左幾十年。搞到生左繡<br />\n邊似得遼寧艦，長期放喺船塢，避風塘。咁D海水咪唔會濺到上船身囉，最多都係水線下生繡"},{"pid":"a417ba083b8a4dec5b58385a4dff7260a2b7fc3d","tid":312394,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"呢啲仲算細節？講野都好保守喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f9f6f9e6eeeba2a31fda4d485d698c15f7679f","tid":312394,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Impressed current cathodic protection system (ICCP)<br />\n<br />\n但燒重油就算鳩數吧啦....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地核動力先玩得起ICCP</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/222031_35c10d432d0a723799091565aa18e5c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F222031_35c10d432d0a723799091565aa18e5c5.jpg&h=c9e489b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生癌五毛唔夠人講就貼D白痴野<br />\n<br />\n等錢醫病呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f6e4c2c1ab877276c4c054906ac0a488328bb0","tid":312394,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"算啦 原本都五勞七傷"},{"pid":"95eb5aa3dd87756a7f5f1059ea08670460cba01a","tid":312394,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"澳門有23條，rip"},{"pid":"bd9a0c34146c71d70577c671a0bee0252cb78723","tid":312394,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <blockquote><blockquote>水線上生鏽同水線下生鏽邊個攞命啲都分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大大張圖自己又唔擘大對屎眼睇<br />\n人地係上面有鏽水流落嚟下面<br />\n支那就直接喺水線打落生鏽<br />\n五毛繼續兜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">haha你真係要..擘大對屎眼慢慢睇，<br />\n兩張相有何不同，船身都會生鏽？<br />\n水線打下無生鏽？識唔識放大相呀，</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/212652_51fa4f4d5c36e54c460ba8d3d88f7665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F212652_51fa4f4d5c36e54c460ba8d3d88f7665.jpg&h=b0aaec9c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">船嘅〈水線〉長期浸在海水中唔會〈生鏽〉？<br />\n船身有幾何有海水浸到？竟會〈生鏽〉？<br />\n你自己擘大啲個屎眼睇清楚，再唔係早啲瞓喇！</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n都係美帝既錯。<br />\n美帝航母唔應該出洋。D海水拍到上甲板。都係美帝維護唔好。俾D海水打左幾十年。搞到生左繡<br />\n邊似得遼寧艦，長期放喺船塢，避風塘。咁D海水咪唔會濺到上船身囉，最多都係水線下生繡</blockquote><br />\n最衰都係美帝<br />\n好地地做咩要喺CV度放艇仔出去<br />\n收返嚟咁多海水搞到生鏽<br />\n啲鏽水又唔爭氣流埋落去<br />\n撩撚號咪幾好<br />\n得水線下面會生鏽<br />\n重要係新船行冇耐就開始鏽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa168707ba056bf02d1e1f9d42581abc4cb4e50","tid":312394,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"張相低清過當年你老母拍嘅咸片<br />\n放大之後黑撚到咁你話係係老母個閪都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65170f911ba68fbf36466e12345cb621a7ad328e","tid":312394,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"d 銹用係最新camo 黎你識d 咩"},{"pid":"f92a1f3cf05087fbec938ec214386b38302d0a3c","tid":312394,"uid":10890,"like"