blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">船嘅〈水線〉長期浸在海水中唔會〈生鏽〉？<br />\n船身有幾何有海水浸到？竟會〈生鏽〉？<br />\n你自己擘大啲個屎眼睇清楚，再唔係早啲瞓喇！</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家啲五毛邊到請返來<br />\n連常識都冇<br />\n空氣有水份又點解唔會令船身生鏽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更何況你支那件垃圾只係落咗水短短幾年<br />\n就生鏽成咁<br />\n擺明係手工差兼有先天缺憾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0082115441535c1363a11ecbc413dd0b2d0c0e05","tid":312394,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G1BANkwGVZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG1BANkwGVZQ&d=eMZntT2KeQ%2FrWnFhImo7sMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=cd8a0845\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G1BANkwGVZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n每次睇親都停唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c0a8e83a029bf0dc6ef12e771119b7f5980be6","tid":312394,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"講保養，大陸真係世界級咁廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以有一流嘅hardware 都可以好快用到殘晒"},{"pid":"336285178c559692b46c05c99aae7f10b71e1f12","tid":312394,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講保養，大陸真係世界級咁廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以有一流嘅hardware 都可以好快用到殘晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為草率同粗糙係北佬文化基因，冇得改，嶺南文化先有精致同靈巧"},{"pid":"52e54da21c64f5b3b1df5124ca9d6749c5e5075b","tid":312394,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"香港送嘅垃圾船都拎黎打飛機,支那人真係世界笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610df0ede7a9536a3a745cd17e5a7d54fc132189","tid":312394,"uid":58862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"依隻船耐過美軍果隻啦<br />\n<br />\n其實保養係唔好 但我見好多國家都唔係保養得好  德國野都見